• Usually, we can only write the δ [简写，只需写产生式]
• Sometimes, Write “G[E]/G(E)” before the production, where G is 
the grammar name and E is the start symbol. [文法名和开始符号]
Grammar [文法]
18
G=< {i, +,*, (, )} ，{E} ，E ，δ >
δ is composed of the following 
production[只含*,+的算术表达式文法]
δ = {E→i; 
E→ E+E; 
E→ E*E; 
E→(E)}
G = {E→i; 
E→ E+E; 
E→ E*E; 
E→(E)}
E→i | E+E | E*E | (E)
G[E]/G(E)/G: 

E→i; 

E→ E+E; 

